{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll never forget that, and that really frightened me, when he-- as we embraced, he said this is a beautiful country.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is a rich country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're going to have a good life and forget what the dirty Nazis did to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that kind of scared me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as a result of that, of course, I began jotting down from memory, in Hungarian-- that was my best language in 1946-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] jot down exactly what I experienced.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I put into a book form.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I actually did was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go to school, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to evening school and at the same time worked for the same uncle of mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I got so by 1947, '48, I was so advanced in my English and my studies that I registered for classes at, at City College of New York.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And education was really the, the biggest drive, the biggest thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted to know, know, knowledge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was hungry for knowledge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was my main thing at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, I went to school to City College and-- but then, part-time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I also worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then the Korean War broke out, of course, and when the Korean broke out-- war broke out, I was drafted in the American Army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it isn't to say that I had no choice, but once, once you're drafted, you have to submit yourself to the draft, which I did.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave them all the details, all the information, including when they asked you, do you have any visible markings on you?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Visible marking?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I have a tattoo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was put down on my forms there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
